## Why This Is Asked

Tests ability to design admission controls that enforce security and resource policies at Pod creation, plus TLS and Kubernetes API wiring.

## Key Concepts

- Validating admission webhook
- PodSpec validation and idempotency
- TLS via Secrets and CA bundles
- ValidatingWebhookConfiguration namespace selectors
- Rollback and test strategies under load

## Code Example

```go
// pseudo Go snippet showing validating logic for resources and image
func validatePod(pod *corev1.Pod) bool {
  for _, c := range pod.Spec.Containers {
    if c.Resources.Requests == nil || c.Resources.Limits == nil {
      return false
    }
    if c.Image != "registry.company.com/allowed" { return false }
    if strings.HasSuffix(c.Image, ":latest") { return false }
  }
  return true
}
```

